cs.IR, cs.CL, cs.DL, cs.DB, cs.AI 

The paper deals with the analysis of user queries in a web analytics tool using information extraction techniques and linked data. This involves natural language processing, semantic analysis, and knowledge bases, which are all relevant to the fields of information retrieval (cs.IR), computational linguistics (cs.CL), deep learning (cs.DL), databases (cs.DB), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper.
